[193.528885, "o", "\r\nFOUND FUSION at position 210!\r\nFusion: eGFP(no stop) + FLAG(no start, no stop) + SNAP(no start, with stop)\r\n\r\nBefore fusion in output: tttaagaaggagatatacat\r\nAfter fusion in output: tgaggatcccgggaattctc\r\n"]
