[604.777526, "o", "\r\n1. Number of primer pairs: 4\r\n   Total primers: 8\r\n\r\n2. Header format check:\r\n   ✓ input_fwd: Correct format\r\n   ✓ input_rev: Correct format\r\n   ✓ egfp_fwd: Correct format\r\n   ✓ egfp_rev: Correct format\r\n   ✓ flag_fwd: Correct format\r\n   ✓ flag_rev: Correct format\r\n   ✓ snap_fwd: Correct format\r\n   ✓ snap_rev: Correct format\r\n\r\n3. Annealing region length and Tm check:\r\n"]
